00:24:42.694 --> 00:24:48.684
For many people, it can seem strange that Americans have such a fascination, and

00:24:49.074 --> 00:24:54.534
almost cult-like obsession with the founding fathers of the country, with the

00:24:54.694 --> 00:25:00.134
